The Home Depot (THD) is a US based Super store. The Employees have been provided with Citi Credit Cards. WHen there is default in the payment by the due date, various process is implemented in the Automated Collection System (ACS) to enable the Collections team to get settle the dues.
The Processes that was in use during 2010-2011 are
Cure,
UPP (Universal Payment Program)
Paydown
Matchpay
